/*!
  \page src_backend_ToHDL_page SystemC, VHDL, Verilog backends

This project contains the classes, data structures, and routines used to create Hardware Description Language (HDL) code from an intermediate representation, usually a circuit representation (see \ref src_circuit_page).
These back ends are used by the PandA synthesis flows to emit SystemC, VHDL, and Verilog outputs.
*/
